        "label": "Effect Additional Information",
        "value": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">During Action Scenes, this communication is limited to 30&rsquo; of information during each of the target&rsquo;s Turns, and if they want to transmit a message during another&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Any Character: NPC or Protagonist\"><abbr title=\"Any Character: NPC or Protagonist\">Character</abbr></abbr>&rsquo;s&nbsp;<abbr title=\"Whenever I play during an Action Scene\"><abbr title=\"Whenever I play during an Action Scene\">Turn</abbr></abbr>, they must spend their&nbsp;<abbr title=\"One slot per Round as a response to another Character's Movement or Action\"><abbr title=\"One slot per Round as a response to another Character's Movement or Action\">Reaction</abbr></abbr>&nbsp;to do so. You can transmit your messages to all your targets at once, but they cannot communicate between them, only through you.</span></p>"
