    "Description": {
      "type": "text",
      "dtype": "String",
      "label": "Metapower Description",
      "value": "<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Progressing further into the labyrinth of telepathic mastery, Manipulators emerge wielding Telepathic Message, a conduit for psychic exchange that transcends the confines of spoken words. Initiation of this process hinges upon focused concentration yet engenders a nexus of mental interaction that unites multiple minds in rapid exchange. As a mental conductor, the Manipulator orchestrates this symphony of thoughts, channeling information through their own consciousness while simultaneously disseminating it among recipients. &nbsp;Accomplished telepaths command this art to facilitate intricate group conversations spanning extended periods and vast distances. A faltering activation might manifest as isolated soliloquies echoing within the recesses of the Manipulator's mind.</span></em></p>"
